{"tid":866654,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"香港教會不會告訴你的基督教聖經和社會真相","createTime":"2018-10-18T04:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T15:39:39.000Z","uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"959eb46314eff71470fa741fca43ec324ccf707e","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:43:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>教會告訴你</strong><br />\n神愛世人，耶穌為世人受苦釘十字架。<br />\n神是公平的，是公義的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>被遺漏的聖經與社會真相</strong><br />\n<br />\n經文（馬太福音13章11至12節）<br />\n<strong>耶穌回答說：「因為天國的奧祕只叫你們知道，不叫他們知道。凡有的，還要加給他，叫他有餘；凡沒有的，連他所有的也要奪去。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n天主教思高聖經版（瑪竇福音 第十三章11至12節）<br />\n<strong>耶穌回答他們說：「因為天國的奧妙，是給你們知道，並不是給他們知道。因為凡有的，還要給他，使他富足；但是，凡沒有的，連他所有的，也要由他奪去。」</strong>["},{"pid":"cba3afb3910da353b20960da3afcf8799b1736d9","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:20:52.000Z","msg":"上帝是公平的，給了你醜陋的外表，還會給你低的智商和垃圾的社交技能，以免讓你顯得不協調。"},{"pid":"237b796046c08c91e1dec80ebfde236247abb066","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"醜小鴨變白天鵝不是因為他有多努力，<br />\n而是因為他父母就是天鵝。<br />\n<br />\n只要是石頭，到那裡去都不會發光。<br />\n<br />\n富人不幸福，窮人更不幸福<br />\n<br />\n錢不能買健康，窮撚錢和健康都冇。"},{"pid":"32c71f292d81d4b2ad76f1e6303582814f2ad6f9","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"上帝是公平的，給了你一張醜臉，一定還會給你一個沒錢的家。<br />\n<br />\n其實你不是一無所有，因為你有的是病。"},{"pid":"f34cdda6436a0c2f24277c09b39aa3cd96fa4717","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:30:59.000Z","msg":"人生就是這樣，有歡笑也有淚水。<br />\n一部分人主要負責歡笑，大部分人主要負責淚水。<br />\n<br />\n所謂熟能生朽嘛。<br />\n負責歡笑的人，就越多歡樂。<br />\n負責淚水的人，就越多淚水。"},{"pid":"49e0ddadfcd2bb55bd919094b356f157939aaec2","tid":866654,"uid":205928,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"樓主個個po都係毒雞湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f62d5329601fa09a19e0720ec1661e6e064501","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e0ddadfcd2bb55bd919094b356f157939aaec2","tid":866654,"uid":205928,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"樓主個個po都係毒雞湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:32:33.000Z","msg":"每post來點負能量"},{"pid":"eef45631b69e3ca61d6c97b19547687d319ce557","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"耶穌說天國的奧秘就是：因為凡有的，還要給他，使他富足；但是，凡沒有的，連他所有的，也要由他奪去。"},{"pid":"ca2c2105163cb44ca735e0da97fe3a307573ae8b","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"香港回歸前<br />\n中國共產黨成日會批評香港是資本主義社會<br />\n貧富懸殊嚴重<br />\n香港窮人的地獄，富人的天堂<br />\n<br />\n回歸後<br />\n香港的貧富懸殊越來越嚴重<br />\n富人更多享受<br />\n窮人更多眼淚"},{"pid":"ab8014c06e1f76869394f1c3d12cfc0be6e7528e","tid":866654,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"樓豬應該會落地肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56a464f5b725b03159317c0c4c079147932827a","tid":866654,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"又一連登仔加入負能量大軍"},{"pid":"ee7ab4c2203bd37d0a2550340e71bc2cca6c8dc3","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:54:38.000Z","msg":"1975年後窮人上流難度激增<br />\n中國人脫貧要等足7代<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180724/bknint-20180724000012203-0724_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180724%2Fbknint-20180724000012203-0724_17011_001.html&d=MhuHPZVxdG7nVaFusxlDhP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a8526239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180724/bknint-20180724000012203-0724_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年7月新聞：<br />\n<br />\n報告分析認為，社會貧富收入不均情況加劇，令基層難以向上爬；跨代貧窮成為常態，父親是低收入人士的話，下一代也有1/3機會是低收入階層。最快可以打破貧窮命運的是北歐國家，如丹麥、芬蘭、挪威、瑞典（約2至3代）；澳洲、英國及美國則是4至5代；中國及印度要7代；南美國家如巴西、及哥倫比亞，則要9至11代。<br />\n<br />\n聽聞香港貧富懸殊比中國大陸和歐美日英澳嚴重得多。"},{"pid":"0b421e25d0497a7ba6726142f3320c233ef8a5fd","tid":866654,"uid":116105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e0ddadfcd2bb55bd919094b356f157939aaec2","tid":866654,"uid":205928,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"樓主個個po都係毒雞湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"樓主好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0617538d8a5c7ee5dc0d235e9f00c35484bebe","tid":866654,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:17:27.000Z","msg":"你斷章取義"},{"pid":"6214c16f6d28c95079089da7fd9f924575eac831","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d0617538d8a5c7ee5dc0d235e9f00c35484bebe","tid":866654,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:17:27.000Z","msg":"你斷章取義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da82de73faf14421f4c346540830023d2d9680a","tid":866654,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d0617538d8a5c7ee5dc0d235e9f00c35484bebe","tid":866654,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:17:27.000Z","msg":"你斷章取義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e3da84e14dee929cb8ee8250e59dbefc0bacfe","tid":866654,"uid":165187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:54:25.000Z","msg":"Pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm